## Burndown Chart

| Color | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| Orange Line | Total Scope |
| Blue Area | Remaining Work |
| Gray Line | Ideal Trend |

### Analysis

ğŸ§  Issues:
- Scope increased mid-sprint  
- Tasks not closed  

ğŸ’¡ Tips:
- Lock scope early  
- Trade-off urgent items  
- Improve planning accuracy  

